1.安装
https://developer.android.com/studio/install

2.配置
https://developer.android.com/studio/intro/studio-config
Appearance:
  打开Show memory indicator，可显示内存占用
  勾选Always show full path in window header可在顶部显示完整文件路径
Notifications:
  关闭Enable system notifications，可在系统托盘中隐藏AS图标
  修改Android Gradle Upgrade Notification为No popup，以免每次打开项目后提示升级Gradle插件
  No popup  不显示弹出框
  Balloon   显示后自动消失
  Sticky balloon  显示后需主动关闭
  https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/settings-notifications.html

3.使用
控制台输出乱码问题，打开Help - Edit Custom VM Options在文件底部加上：
-Dfile.encoding=UTF-8

4.常用插件
Translation
https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/8579-translation
